To download directly (e.g. if you want to download it with wget command) follow these steps:
download the file and upload it:
 - on file.io (free version link valid for 1 download)
 - on gdrive, then go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ ; create/open a project ; enable gdrive api ; create an APIKey ; replace the FileID and APIKey in the below URL
   (find the FileID in the sharing url of the file, i.e. in the above public link is 1USwKGGfFbcl9rwzQ2AgMBwVUBMm2Pfui)

https://www.googleapis.com/drive/v3/files/FileID?alt=media&key=APIKey

then from cmd:
> wget "https://www.googleapis.com/drive/v3/files/FileID?alt=media&key=APIKey
> unzip thefile.zip

